    "Fourth, one of the first AI models capable of disempowering humanity is also able to stop other actors from building other AI models capable of disempowering humanity or, failing that, stop these models from disempowering humanity.",
    "While I hope that all these conditions obtain, one cannot take this for granted and it seems relatively unlikely.",
    "To summarize, while there is hope that the alignment problem is less hard than it seems, it is likely that the problem is very difficult.",
